data.description: Come by and see your new home today. RANCH HOME -This 4-year-old duplex offers modern living and convenience all on one Level.   You will feel the openness of the cathedral ceilings in the great room and kitchen area.  Enjoy the eat-in kitchen with a breakfast bar, plenty of cabinets, and kitchen appliances included. Home Featuring 3 spacious bedrooms, the Large main bedroom ensuite. Finished Laundry/Mudroom leads to the attached 2-car garage up at the front of the home, and at the back, a sliding glass door leads to a concrete patio with a partially fenced backyard off the kitchen area for your enjoyment. Fences are allowed, there are low HOA fees, and it is convenient for grocery stores, restaurants, and entertainment centers. Expressway access close by
